      <title>荷兰国王面临因税收提案损失一半薪水的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/dutch-king-willem-alexander-risks-losing-half-his-paycheck-to-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰国王威廉-亚历山大正面临失去一半薪水的边缘，因为该国议会准备就一项对他的收入征税的提案进行投票——就像他的臣民一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/dutch-king-willem-alexander-risks-losing-half-his-paycheck-to-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 18:57:28 GMT</pubDate>
